::Havoc::

Havoc turns around, sighing at the banging from the CR. He taps a
button on a console and speaks into the microphone that pops out.

"Allright, if you agree to be good, we'll let you out. You're in the
Alliance base, not Maximals or Predacon, so act good."

The words were played back in the CR for Wolfgang to hear.
